  "api": {
    "url": "POST /api/v1/datacenter/analysis/account-performance/platform-performance-placeholder-table",
    "method": "POST",
    "priority": "P1",
    "requestBody": "currentPage, dateStart, dateEnd, kw, ownerId, pageSize, appIds, source",
    "responseBody": "code, message, data { platformTotal, accountTotal, platforms }；platforms[].firstThreeDayRoi 为 { dates, data }，一日一点"
  },
  "apiSuggestion": {
    "notes": [
      "HTTP 层统一包装为 code / message / data；业务字段在 data 内。",
      "firstThreeDayRoi 为 dates + data：三日则长度为 3，一日一个 ROI，对应一条折线；对接 ECharts 时 xAxis.data = dates，series[0].data = data。若将来要同一图里多条对比线再扩展为 series 数组。",
      "iconBg/iconColor/iconChar 用于前端徽章；usageRate 可能大于 100；roi3/roi7 可与折线并存。",
      "若前端底部文案由 platforms 汇总，请与 accountTotal 对齐口径。"
    ]
  }
}
